window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The international best seller - don't compete without it! </p> <p>A major best seller in Japan, <i>Financial Times</i> top-ten book of the year, Book-of-the-Month Club best seller, and required reading at the best business schools, <i>Thinking Strategically</i> is a crash course in outmaneauvering any rival. This entertaining guide builds on scores of case studies taken from business, sports, the movies, politics, and gambling. It outlines the basics of good strategy-making and then shows how you can apply them in any area of your life.</p>"; 
